      "writtenOn": "2020-06-23T21:14:36Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Did you consider just memory-mapping the file? https://godoc.org/golang.org/x/exp/mmap and https://golang.org/pkg/io/#NewSectionReader\n\nI think this would effectively have the same effect, but you\u0027d let the OS do the memory buffering.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 38,
        "startChar": 8,
        "endLine": 38,
        "endChar": 27
      },
      "revId": "703e004cf80296ba86af00a458dc07080a646505",
